invalid type: string "Page 21 of 22 \n \n11. Annexures - Definitions \nTerm Description \nElectric \nVehicles (EV) \nEVs comprise battery electric vehicles (BEV), plug -in electric vehicles \n(PEV), plug -in hybrid electric vehicles (PHEV) and strong hybrid \nelectric vehicles (SHEV). \nEV \nComponents \nmeans components of  \n• EV including Motor Controller, Electric Engine (motor) for EV,  \ne